{"tid":1438572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「新口號」","createTime":"2019-08-09T20:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T20:27:36.000Z","uid":281318,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7bce2972d873529d9581b4d02bd06f1ab6447ab6","tid":1438572,"uid":281318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:24:43.000Z","msg":"唔想再衝擊，追取撤實釋<br />\n<br />\n訓唔著，諗左個口號，有無得試下，既然光復香港，時代革命會不得人心，又唔夠巨體，不如就直接擺5大訴求切句野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n追：追究黑警濫捕<br />\n取：取消暴動定性<br />\n撤：撤回逃犯條例<br />\n實：實行雙普選<br />\n釋：釋放義士<br />\n<br />\n文宣上係句野下加行細字，令人先明白句野意義，叫慣左就可以長用，始終要對準政府同5大訴求，已經比林鄭推左係經濟，再同班警犬糾纏無作為，比佢推左落比商家佬度，到時人民對人民，然後勇武對和理非，就會2014重演，我地唔可以再輸！我地有幾廿人比佢地告暴動，之前咁多義士離開我地！我地無理由再輸比個八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1ee62771c393d390c2b9294148fd5bd6963d6c","tid":1438572,"uid":105699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:25:27.000Z","msg":"改你老母呀"},{"pid":"5cb50259c11773e6d4bd00700e052ee3edf298de","tid":1438572,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:26:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dee9fb67ced0ea57889e016ee870ddff7b1242","tid":1438572,"uid":28770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:27:36.000Z","msg":"你噏乜9啊你"}]}